// Regression: libFuzzer, 2026-04-17. Input `enum::` caused ParseEnum's
// variant loop to spin forever — Consume(IDENTIFIER) failed without advancing
// current, every iteration allocated a variant node, arena exhausted.
// Fix: progress guard in ParseEnum's variant loop (bwsl_parser_soa.cpp).
// Expected: compiler exits cleanly with a parse error, not a crash or hang.
enum::
